extends layout

block content
    style.
        .terms-card {
            border-radius: 24px;
            background: #ffffff;
        }
        .terms-section {
            padding-left: 20px;
            border-left: 3px solid #f1f5f9;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        .terms-section:hover {
            border-left-color: #0f172a;
            background: #f8fafc;
            border-top-right-radius: 12px;
            border-bottom-right-radius: 12px;
        }
        .summary-box {
            background: #f8fafc;
            border: 1px dashed #cbd5e1;
            border-radius: 16px;
        }
        .prohibited-list li {
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            position: relative;
            list-style: none;
        }
        .prohibited-list li::before {
            content: "✕";
            color: #ef4444;
            font-weight: bold;
            position: absolute;
            left: -20px;
        }

    .container.mt-5.mb-5
        //- ===== HEADER =====
        .text-center.mb-5
            span.badge.bg-primary.bg-opacity-10.text-primary.px-3.py-2.rounded-pill.mb-3.small.fw-bold Guidelines
            h1.fw-bold Terms & Conditions
            p.text-muted Please read these rules for using our platform

        .row.justify-content-center
            .col-lg-9
                .card.terms-card.border-0.shadow-lg
                    .card-body.p-4.p-md-5
                        
                        //- QUICK SUMMARY
                        .summary-box.p-4.mb-5
                            h6.fw-bold.mb-2 💡 TL;DR (Too Long; Didn't Read)
                            p.small.text-muted.mb-0
                                | Be honest, be respectful, and take care of the items you borrow. ShareLoop is a platform to help you connect, but you are responsible for your own interactions and safety.

                        //- SECTION: Usage
                        .terms-section.mb-5.p-3
                            h5.fw-bold 👤 Platform Usage
                            p.text-muted.lh-base
                                | To maintain a safe community, you must provide accurate information when creating an account. You are solely responsible for keeping your login credentials secure and for all activity that occurs under your account.

                        //- SECTION: Responsibilities
                        .terms-section.mb-5.p-3
                            h5.fw-bold 🤝 User Responsibilities
                            p.text-muted.lh-base
                                | ShareLoop is built on trust. Users are responsible for the accuracy of their listings, the condition of the items they lend, and returning borrowed items in the same state they were received.

                        //- SECTION: Prohibited
                        .terms-section.mb-5.p-3
                            h5.fw-bold 🚫 Prohibited Activities
                            p.text-muted By using the platform, you agree to refrain from:
                            ul.text-muted.prohibited-list.ms-3
                                li Fraudulent or misleading listings
                                li Harassment, abusive behavior, or discrimination
                                li Any activity that violates local laws
                                li Attempting to bypass the platform's security

                        //- SECTION: Platform Role
                        .terms-section.mb-5.p-3
                            h5.fw-bold ⚖️ Our Role & Liability
                            p.text-muted.lh-base
                                | ShareLoop acts as a facilitator. While we strive to maintain a safe community, **ShareLoop is not responsible for the transactions, damage to items, or disputes between users.** We provide the tools, but the community provides the trust.

                        //- SECTION: Updates
                        .terms-section.mb-5.p-3
                            h5.fw-bold 🔄 Updates to Terms
                            p.text-muted.lh-base.mb-0
                                | We may update these terms to reflect changes in our service or the law. Continued use of ShareLoop after an update constitutes your acceptance of the new terms.

                        hr.my-5.opacity-10

                        .d-flex.justify-content-between.align-items-center.flex-wrap.gap-3
                            p.text-muted.small.mb-0
                                | Last updated: **#{new Date().getFullYear()}**
                            a.btn.btn-outline-dark.btn-sm.rounded-pill(href="/contact") 
                                | Have a question? Contact us

        //- NAVIGATION LINK
        .text-center.mt-4
            a.text-muted.small.text-decoration-none(href="/privacy-policy") 
                | ← View Privacy Policy